Weezy?

08:12.707 --> 08:13.841
You're alive!

08:13.892 --> 08:15.476
Yeah, thanks to Sue.
She's a miracle worker.

08:15.543 --> 08:17.311
Oh, well, it's amazing
what a little TLC,

08:17.379 --> 08:19.546
