number.

08:24.236 --> 08:25.486
Oh, screw that.

08:25.553 --> 08:27.221
This is our last time
performing together.

08:27.272 --> 08:29.156
You're doing it,
and so you are you, Tina.

08:29.224 --> 08:31.058
